The paper also discusses optimization and generalization, which are important topics in ML, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely. Additionally, the paper uses visualization techniques, which are commonly used in computer vision (CV) and neural networks (NE), so cs.CV and cs.NE are also possible categories.
